creator: Rudyard Kipling
description:
LibriVox recording of The Jungle Book (Version 3) by Rudyard Kipling.
Read in English by Shiloh Fuscello; Mike Cantrell; Ezwa; Digs; Steve Owen; Rachel; Louise Cambau; Vanessa Cooley; Michele Fry; Andy Walla; Pardeep Ahluwalia; Bev J Stevens

A story of a boy who raised by Indian wolves becomes lord of the jungle. (Summary by Jessie Yun)


For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
